{"word":"λιγυρός 1","slug":"λιγυρός 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n63103\" key=\"liguro/s1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λῐγῠρός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ά</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Boeot.\">Boeot.</a></gram> </gramGrp> fem. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λιγουρά</orth> (q.v.), <sense id=\"n63103.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">clear, shrill</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὦρτο δὲ κῦμα πνοιῇ ὕπο λιγυρῇ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:215\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.215</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:526\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.526</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:590\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.590</biblScope> </bibl>; of a whip, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:532\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.532</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:242\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">242</biblScope> </bibl> (anap.); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀκόνα</foreign> (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=